message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would significantly enhance your business operations. Given its value to you, we are confident it will be a worthwhile investment. I am offering this exceptional item to you at a special price of $14,000, which I believe strikes a balance between fair market value and a reasonable profit margin for us. Please let me know if you are interested in proceeding with this offer. We look forward to potentially working with you.
